es/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T10:14:09.000Z","msg":"問下你地意見都唔撚得咁撚惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T10:16:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://the-sun.on.cc/channels/news/20020914/20020914033737_0001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthe-sun.on.cc%2Fchannels%2Fnews%2F20020914%2F20020914033737_0001.html&d=6zgGjWaceJ4ICz2LU8gYzrtp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=364a7a6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://the-sun.on.cc/channels/news/20020914/20020914033737_0001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n百黑漢圍警圖搶犯<br />\n夜拉隊叫囂 元朗警署落閘<br />\n<br />\n  14/09/2002<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】元朗「十&times;K」及「和&times;和」兩大黑幫昨晨在同一時間內訌大曬馬，打亂警力部署，釀成警員被百名黑漢包圍和企圖搶犯大騷亂。當警方集中警力鎮壓「和&times;和」內訌時，「十&times;K」兩名老叔父各自「吹雞」，黑漢多過警員，當街毆鬥及衝擊警員，有人恐嚇記者和企圖趁亂劫走被捕的同門兄弟，警方需急抽調其他分區警力<em>馳援</em>鎮亂，大批警員揮動伸縮警棍追捕涉案兇徒，拘捕五名男子。<br />\n<br />\n-----"},{"pid":"cdf3e4ed5015683b85e6015bb79a841f62965048","tid":2236184,"uid":188310,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T10:16:54.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">咁恆馳呢</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f7a862534761c3f286652291653cf35e81e0396","tid":2236184,"uid":327462,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T10:17:22.000Z","msg":"係唔係蝗語就唔知<br />\n但係肯定香港人唔會用"},{"pid":"2eeff9ff5192695e6e7f8d512c88961b45a04822","tid":2236184,"uid":88743,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6a2a0b0e051547307c0bb883b23a185059fd43c2","tid":2236184,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T10:12:06.000Z","msg":"書面語，但南方小用印象中"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T10:18:15.000Z","msg":"係時候被同化<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咱們都是中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" clas